#{{chemistry}} In [[organic chemistry]], a [[divalent]] [[functional group]], (-CO-), characteristic of [[aldehyde]]s, [[ketone]]s, [[carboxylic acid]]s, [[amide]]s, [[carboxylic acid anhydride]]s, [[carbonyl halide]]s, [[ester]]s and others
#{{chemistry}} Any [[compound]] of a [[metal]] with [[carbon monoxide]], such as [[nickel carbonyl]], Ni(CO)<sub>4</sub>

